   6:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *
   7:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *   This file provides two functions and one global variable to be called from 
   8:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *   user application:
   9:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *      - SystemInit(): This function is called at startup just after reset and 
  10:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                      before branch to main program. This call is made inside
  11:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                      the "startup_stm32f4xx.s" file.
  12:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *
  13:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *      - SystemCoreClock variable: Contains the core clock (HCLK), it can be used
  14:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                                  by the user application to setup the SysTick 
  15:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                                  timer or configure other parameters.
  16:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                                     
  17:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *      - SystemCoreClockUpdate(): Updates the variable SystemCoreClock and must
  18:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                                 be called whenever the core clock is changed
  19:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                                 during program execution.
  20:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *
  21:Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32F4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *
